## ğŸ”„ PHASE 8: PAGE DISCOVERY SYSTEM (5 min)

### **TEST 8.1: Check Discovered Pages in DB**

**Location:** Neon SQL Editor

**Steps:**
```sql
SELECT 
  a.name as agency,
  COUNT(wp.id) as pages_found
FROM agencies a
LEFT JOIN website_pages wp ON a.id = wp.agency_id
GROUP BY a.id, a.name
ORDER BY pages_found DESC;
```

**Expected Result:**
```
âœ… Shows agencies with page counts
âœ… Some agencies have pages > 0
âœ… Or all = 0 (if discovery not run yet)
```

**Pass/Fail:** [ ] Pass [ ] Fail

---

### **TEST 8.2: View Discovered Pages Detail**

**Steps:**
```sql
SELECT 
  page_url,
  page_type,
  word_count,
  times_scanned,
  last_score
FROM website_pages
WHERE agency_id = 1
ORDER BY times_scanned DESC, last_scanned_at DESC;
```

**Expected Result:**
```
âœ… Shows pages for agency
âœ… URLs visible
âœ… Types: homepage, blog, service, etc.
âœ… Word counts shown
âœ… Times scanned = 0 (if not scanned yet)
```

**Pass/Fail:** [ ] Pass [ ] Fail

